Buy low and sell high is the basics and that never changes.

$AAPL $NVDA $AMZN $FB $NFLX

It’s true that $FAANG has been bearish these last couple of weeks. But these stock prices do not reflect performance. 

Q4 should heed strong performance for $AMZN $AAPL $NVDA. Expect a rally leading up to earnings as the market shakes off the noise.

All these talks of big money institutions moving money from big tech to cyclical is valid. 

But as big tech stock prices fall that will only invite big money to jump in on the opportunity. The fundamentals persevere regardless of the situation: buy on the dip.
